,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lk0-ugtT_68\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLk0-ugtT_68&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=a1560268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lk0-ugtT_68</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔俾我留言宣洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b91231fb93210ccf8107afd50726fc09421ee8","tid":1738760,"uid":128991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"想個個捐款者親身去office屌人？"},{"pid":"ae222c9b3740f3b700a967555442f2c527a4f3ec","tid":1738760,"uid":322689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0bf6f3ba156083f674e7ebf5fcd0161785eaeec","tid":1738760,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"銀行app入面有得管理自動轉賬<br />\n大家自己識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（暫時手足話hsbc同boc都得）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"無國界醫生熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut，我以HSBC為例，做法係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先登入HSBC網上理財（一定要電腦版，電話app不能）<br />\n2. 然後喺 &quot;我的銀行&quot; 欄目下揀 &quot;自動轉賬 &quot;<br />\n3. 揀 &quot;管理自動轉賬&quot;，然後就會見到你每月要轉賬嘅項目<br />\n4. 揀返 &quot;Medecins Sans F HK L&quot;，然後 &quot;刪除指示&quot; 再確認<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以成功cut捐款，但我唔知其他銀行網上理財係咪一樣，大家即管試吓！<br />\n<br />\n唔捐都唔夠，要攞返之前捐過嘅錢！方法如下：<br />\n可以打上card centre要求charge back返晒之前所有捐款<br />\nchargeback除咗攞返錢，商戶係要食好貴手續費<br />\n(chargeback 只限 credit card）"},{"pid":"00a9e05c4a9236854d2bbdd7f6ec49d2b86c6b45","tid":1738760,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5169093081c6aeb2383469efd9d8bfb65441e574","tid":1738760,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f463450e4a275d2e92e8776b976ca912cc1c45b5","tid":1738760,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lk0-ugtT_68\" d